\   Category: Sound
\    Summary: Phrases for the Watford Electronics Beeb Speech Synthesiser
\  Deep dive: Secrets of the Executive version
\
\ ******************************************************************************

.SPEECH

IF _EXECUTIVE

 EQUB 13

 EQUS "TALK "           \ 1: "Incoming missile"
 EQUS "A NN1 "
